descriptionHtml:
On SteamWorkshop : http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=222278682

=====Description=====

Better Aela The Huntress is a simple mod that change the face
of Aela the Huntress, she don't have WarPaint and have a better
face.

=====Compatibility====

Not compatible with other change Aela mods.

=====Enjoy==========

Just drag the content of Data to yout Data folder
and Enjoy !
Rate it please !
author: MrBrenan
